{"tid":1998630,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"淡淡圍爐區，又有人撻訂了","createTime":"2020-05-02T13:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T11:32:23.000Z","uid":140140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"276ec463ebd798a8a6f90726dbeff3bb03a158d8","tid":1998630,"uid":140140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"本港疫情稍為緩和，但經濟前景存在不明朗因素，加上失業率攀升等不同因素，有新盤買家看淡後市，選擇撻訂離場。繼新地（0016）大埔白石角雲滙早前連環錄得撻大訂個案後，嘉華（0173）同位於白石角的新入伙盤嘉熙，新近亦錄10宗撻大訂個案，而有關單位的買家大多採用建築期付款，買家已繳付樓價10%或15%，而發展商合共殺訂逾1240萬元。"},{"pid":"c57e0b790046da43f71351bb9ae2a0fb195a3568","tid":1998630,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"Aa做數"},{"pid":"dddc03a101ac184d1b6b5f0c7f5c550f11236074","tid":1998630,"uid":6297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"即係搵唔到銀行上會啦！明知樓價只升不跌都唔搵財仔上會。撻定15% 差唔多成球野"},{"pid":"1b373aca94eeaf17d32ab71131ba257fd9e33ad9","tid":1998630,"uid":49797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"係睇淡樓市定睇淡白石角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c05a354c54ff3631f1cf70a721e5f30de36b734","tid":1998630,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"傻左？<br />\n井噴式上升喎 幾大都去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7bc85cda7e9b8f70f33b0d269092a12617796d","tid":1998630,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚買樓 卜街 唔好係連登講野<br />\n連燈好多地產狗搵食</span></span>"}]}